data.description: Seller offering $5k towards closing costs!!! Open house 11/18/23, 12-3pm!! Escape to your personal haven in Navarre, Florida, where a newly renovated 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home awaits on over 1 acre of pristine land. Nestled amidst nature's beauty, this property provides the perfect balance of modern comfort and peaceful serenity. Step inside the 1,040 sqft interior, where sunlight pours in through updated energy-efficient windows from 2014, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open living space is perfect for relaxation and entertaining, offering a flexible layout for your personal touch. A highlight of this home is the kitchen, where all-new appliances, installed in May of this year, shine against a backdrop of modern design. Enjoy year-round comfort with a new air conditioning unit (2021) and the peace of mind that comes with a new roof (2015). As you step outside, you're greeted by over 1 acre of land, providing endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment. Whether it's gardening, expanding the property, or simply savoring the tranquility, this vast space is a blank canvas for your dreams. This unique Navarre gem offers a private retreat while being conveniently located near local schools, pristine beaches, and essential amenities. Embrace the coastal lifestyle and make this property your own tranquil escape. Don't miss this opportunity to secure your slice of paradise!
